         <abstract id="aspace_ae593b2e0b5cd8697c231eb84ab1c41a">The records consist of reports and resolutions documenting the activities of the Yale Club of New York City. Included are a report of Committee of Inquiry, a resolution regarding the deaths of William Dwight Whitney and James Dwight Dana (1895), and a report on commemorative tablets for the Daughters of the American Revolution (1970).</abstract>
