      <scopecontent id="aspace_565986f00e6ac03990d90f19121deb37">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of reports and resolutions documenting the activities of the Yale Club of New York City. Included are a report of Committee of Inquiry, a resolution regarding the deaths of William Dwight Whitney and James Dwight Dana (1895), and a report on commemorative tablets for the Daughters of the American Revolution (1970).</p>  
      </scopecontent>
